<p><strong>Joseph</strong><em> – 17 years old</em></p>
<p>Joseph’s a very caring young man who loves to make people laugh.He’s always quick to tell a joke and he’s great at first impressions. He has a talent for putting people at ease and wants to help people when he grows up by being a police officer. Joseph believes it’s important to stay healthy. He’d love for his family to join him in outdoor activities like swimming, bike riding and horseback riding. When he’s not outside, he likes to watch his favorite show, Johnny Test.Joseph sometimes has trouble expressing himself and needs a patient and loving family that will understand him and advocate for him in school.He looks forward to making a difference in the world and wants a consistent, caring and supportive family that will enjoy helping him help others!</p>
<p>Please contact Sarah Guy at <a href="mailto:Sarah.Guy@pfsf.org">Sarah.Guy@pfsf.org</a>or 352.244.1655for additional information on this youth.</p>
